WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:11.000
This is the nerve centre we would build for Shell. One live view of the network: active trips, on-time delivery, open exceptions, DG risk holds and ePOD capture. Here, the platform has flagged a trip approaching a school-zone geofence. Let's open it.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Every trip carries a live route-risk score, with the exact contributing factors. Alongside it: driver readiness, vehicle and load checks, and ETA confidence. The risk is high, so we review the hold.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:36.000
The AI recommends a hold and reroute, with the impact quantified before anyone commits. A human controller approves. The decision is logged, instantly and immutably.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:46.000
The reroute executes around the geofence. Driver notified, site rescheduled, customer informed. Automatically.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:57.000
And when the trip closes, the evidence pack has already built itself: permits, inspections, ePOD, reconciliation, invoice match. The scorecard proves the outcomes.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:03.000
One nerve centre. Every trip governed.
